snippet.title: Voidtrain - Exclusive Steam Release Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2022
snippet.description:
Check out the new creatures, features, and islands coming to Voidtrain when the game releases on Steam on October 22nd.

Defend your train from terrifying void creatures as you ride the rails from island to island and build defenses, solve puzzles, and embrace the void with up to four players in co-op. Check out this Voidtrain gameplay, and choose from a variety of weapons and strategies to try and escape the void.

#IGN #IGNSummerofGaming
